// Description of the project


The sense hat will display a line pointing in the direction of magnetic north.
A second line is provided parallel and will turn in the plane with respect to the vertical axis as the user turns/
When the user is facing the primary direction of travel they must press down on the joy stick to lock in the direction
Now a third line will diplay that will show error in direction traveled. 
If the user wants to set a new angle they press down to unlock and down again to set new angle
WHen the user wants to end the program they press down twice quickly
